116
00:11:49,308 --> 00:11:52,402
- I'll go in the back and calm them down.
- Got it.

117
00:11:54,513 --> 00:11:57,539
Hello again, ladies.

118
00:11:57,650 --> 00:12:00,585
As the frequent fliers
amongst you can probably tell...

119
