166
00:17:55,307 --> 00:17:57,707
- I'm okay.
- You all right?

167
00:17:57,809 --> 00:18:00,505
Are you hurt?

168
00:18:00,612 --> 00:18:02,512
Dr. Gerber's on board.

169
00:18:02,614 --> 00:18:05,447
Where is he?

170
